<html>
ACC-Australian Crime Commission-new gestapo born in secret.<br>
JOHN Howard has brokered a deal for a new national law enforcement body,
with two controversial Carr government advisers helping him clinch an
agreement with the states.<br><br>
<table border=3D0>
<tr><td width=3D1><td width=3D302></td><td width=3D1></td></tr>
<tr><td width=3D1><td width=3D302><font size=3D2>Advertisement</font></td><t=
d width=3D1></td></tr>
<tr><td width=3D1><td width=3D302></td><td width=3D1></td></tr>
<tr><td width=3D1><td width=3D302></td><td width=3D1></td></tr>
